{Name}{}{Dusty.}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see a dullish guy, wiping a glass.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{It's a bartender.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{It's a rough guy, with crooked nose and rumpled ears, as if he was boxing formerly. }
